OL,3,GNEWSCUK Government plans for
OL,4,Cterrestrial TV switch-off
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe UK Government is drawing up plans
OL,7,Fto end traditional terrestrial
OL,8,Ftelevision broadcasts and move the
OL,9,Fcountry entirely to streaming,
OL,10,Faccording to reports in The Telegraph.
OL,12,FThe proposals, which apparently have
OL,13,Falready been signed off by Culture
OL,14,FSecretary Lisa Nandy and Technology
OL,15,FSecretary Liz Kendall, are expected to
OL,16,Fbe set out in a green paper due in the
OL,17,Fcoming weeks.
OL,23,EPub: 19-May-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,150,140,200,120,0,100
