OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F149A1782249088
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSCUK Government plans for
OL,4,Cterrestrial TV switch-off
OL,5,
OL,6,FWhile current legislation protects
OL,7,Fterrestrial TV until at least 2034, the
OL,8,Fgovernment is considering an earlier
OL,9,Ftransition ` provided a series of
OL,10,Fsafeguards are met.
OL,12,FThese include nationwide access to
OL,13,Faffordable superfast broadband,
OL,14,Feasy-to-use streaming interfaces, and
OL,15,Fdedicated support for those who
OL,16,Fstruggle with the changeover.
OL,23,EPub: 19-May-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,150,140,200,120,0,100
