OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F149A1782249088
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSCUK Government plans for
OL,4,Cterrestrial TV switch-off
OL,5,
OL,6,FMajor public service broadcasters
OL,7,Fincluding the BBC, ITV, and Channel 4
OL,8,Fare firmly behind the move, citing the
OL,9,Fsignificant cost of maintaining the
OL,10,Fenergy-intensive network of
OL,11,Ftransmitters.
OL,13,FThey are already preparing through a
OL,14,Fjoint venture called Freely ` a
OL,15,Fstreaming platform designed to replace
OL,16,FFreeview, complete with plug-in sticks
OL,17,Ffor older televisions.
OL,19,FHowever, the transition is not without
OL,20,Fcontroversy.
OL,23,EPub: 19-May-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,150,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14904
SC,0004
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F149A1782249088
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSCUK Government plans for
OL,4,Cterrestrial TV switch-off
OL,5,
OL,6,FCampaigners have pushed for the
OL,7,Fterrestrial deadline to be put back to
OL,8,Fat least 2040, warning that older and
OL,9,Fmore vulnerable viewers risk being left
OL,10,Fbehind.
OL,12,FThe government has also acknowledged
OL,13,Fthat around one million households
OL,14,Fcurrently struggle to afford even the
OL,15,Fcheapest broadband tariffs, and is
OL,16,Fexploring potential subsidies to
OL,17,Faddress this.
OL,19,FThe move is heavily dependent on the
OL,20,Frollout of full-fibre broadband across
OL,21,Fthe UK ` a target the government has
OL,22,Fset for 2032.
OL,23,EPub: 19-May-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,150,140,200,120,0,100
