OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSCUK Government plans for
OL,4,Cterrestrial TV switch-off
OL,5,
OL,6,FBroadcasters are working alongside
OL,7,Ftelecoms firms and major high street
OL,8,Fbanks to build the case that the
OL,9,Fdigital switchover will bring wider
OL,10,Feconomic and social benefits.
OL,12,FSeparately, The Telegraph reports that
OL,13,Fa review has also been launched into
OL,14,Fthe future of FM radio, with the
OL,15,Fcommercial radio industry pressing for
OL,16,Fclarity on whether its signals could
OL,17,Falso be switched off during the 2030s.
OL,23,EPub: 19-May-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
